## Runtime.ResourceTree.ReadOnlyResourceTreeLeaf class

Implementation of a read-only resource tree leaf node that contains a resource value. Leaf nodes represent the actual resources in the tree and cannot have children.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare class ReadOnlyResourceTreeLeaf<T> implements IReadOnlyResourceTreeLeaf<T> 
```
**Implements:** [IReadOnlyResourceTreeLeaf](./ts-res.runtime.resourcetree.ireadonlyresourcetreeleaf.md)<!-- -->&lt;T&gt;
